---
title: Tex-Mex Crumbed Pork & Celery Slaw with Crushed Sweetcorn Potatoes & Parsley
description: You can jazz up anything with a bit of bling, like these crushed potatoes, simply add golden corn to the mix and
they are ready to make mouths water. Another example, a crunchy crumb to Mexican spiced pork does wonders
to make this dinner stand out from the crowd!
